      "content": "i know you aren't a doctor but i just want to know if it's actually safe to do that. i mean, 400mg isn't a huge dose, right? i'm thinking of doing this for the next 12 hours or so just to get through the workday. is there any reason why i shouldn't just take them every 2 hours to stay ahead of the inflammation?",
